    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies version 3 of the Remote Procedure Call (RPC) security protocol (RPCSEC_GSS).  This protocol provides support for multi-principal authentication of client hosts and user principals to a server (constructed by generic composition), security label assertions for multi-level security and type enforcement, structured privilege assertions, and channel bindings.  This document updates RFC 5403.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
